\c 150
\s Rumbidzai Jehovha!
\p
\v 1 Harcruya! Rumbidzai Jehovha panzvimbo yake tsvene; Murumbidzei mudenga rakaitwa nesimba rake,
\v 2 Murumbidzei nokuda kwezvaakaita nesimba rake; Murumbidzei zvakafanira ukuru-kuru hwake.
\v 3 Murumbidzei nemitengeranwa nembira.
\v 4 Murumbidzei nengoma nokutamba; Murumbidzei nohudimbwa nenyere.
\v 5 Murumbidzei namakandira anorira kwazvo;
\s Murumbidzei namakandira anorira zvakanaka.
\p
\v 6 Zvinhu zvose zvinofema, ngazvirumbidze Jehovha.
\s Hareruya!
